## Why This Is Asked

Tests understanding of real-time data ingestion on GCP, basic data validation, idempotency via insertId, and integration between Pub/Sub and BigQuery using a simple Cloud Function. Emphasizes low-ops design, immutable inserts, and basic testing.

## Key Concepts

