## Why This Is Asked
This question evaluates the ability to design a region-aware ingestion pipeline with clear boundaries, idempotency, and compliance considerations—common constraints in real-world telemetry systems.

## Key Concepts
- Event-driven architecture using Cloud Functions triggered by GCS object finalize events
- Region-based routing via a multi-bucket strategy
- BigQuery audit logging with composite insertId to ensure idempotent writes
- IAM least-privilege principles for secure access control
- Test planning to validate cross-region data routing

## Code Example
```java
// Cloud Function triggered on GCS object finalize
public class TelemetryRouter implements BackgroundFunction<CloudEvent> {
    private final Storage storage = StorageOptions.getDefaultInstance().getService();
    private final BigQuery bigquery = BigQueryOptions.getDefaultInstance().getService();

    @Override
    public void accept(CloudEvent event, Context context) {
        String bucket = event.getBucket();
        String objectName = event.getObjectName();

        if (!bucket.equals("raw-telemetry")) return;

        String content = new String(storage.get(bucket, objectName).getContent());

        for (String line : content.split("\n")) {
            JsonNode record = new ObjectMapper().readTree(line);
            validateSchema(record);

            String region = record.get("region").asText();
            String targetBucket = region.equals("us") ? "telemetry-us" : "telemetry-eu";
            String destPath = LocalDate.now().format(DateTimeFormatter.ofPattern("yyyy/MM/dd")) + "/" + objectName;

            storage.get(targetBucket, destPath).getWriter().write(record.toString());

            String insertId = objectName + "_" + LocalDate.now() + "_" + region;
            insertAuditLog(insertId, record, targetBucket);
        }
    }

    private void validateSchema(JsonNode record) {
        requireNonNull(record.get("region"), "Missing region field");
        requireNonNull(record.get("timestamp"), "Missing timestamp field");
        // Additional field validation...
    }

    private void insertAuditLog(String insertId, JsonNode record, String targetBucket) {
        TableId tableId = TableId.of("audit", "telemetry_routing_log");
        InsertAllRequest.Builder builder = InsertAllRequest.newBuilder(tableId);
        builder.addRow(Stream.of(
            "insertId", insertId,
            "region", record.get("region").asText(),
            "destination", targetBucket,
            "processedAt", Instant.now().toString()
        ).collect(Collectors.toMap(e -> e[0], e -> e[1])));
        bigquery.insertAll(builder.build());
    }
}
